---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for Construction industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      Construction systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Deal Sourcing -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Project Scheduling & Coordination" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Project Scheduling & Coordination</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified project schedule that connects all crews, subcontractors, and suppliers. Real-time schedule visibility shows daily priorities, surfaces conflicts before they create delays, and coordinates material delivery with installation timing.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Master schedule creation and tracking</li>
            <li>Crew and subcontractor coordination</li>
            <li>Material delivery synchronization</li>
            <li>Daily task assignments</li>
            <li>Schedule conflict alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Underwriting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Budget Tracking & Cost Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Budget Tracking & Cost Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time budget tracking that captures labor, materials, and equipment costs as they occur on site. Identifies cost overruns instantly instead of after project closeout, enabling immediate corrective action.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Activity-level budget tracking</li>
            <li>Cost variance monitoring</li>
            <li>Equipment and material cost capture</li>
            <li>Labor cost tracking by task</li>
            <li>Budget forecast and trending</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Portfolio Analytics -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Change Order Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Change Order Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified change order workflow that documents requests, routes for approval, calculates cost and schedule impact, and communicates decisions to all stakeholders. Eliminates delays and disputes over scope changes.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Change request submission</li>
            <li>Approval routing and tracking</li>
            <li>Cost and schedule impact analysis</li>
            <li>Communication to stakeholders</li>
            <li>Change order documentation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Investor Reporting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Crew & Workforce Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Crew & Workforce Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Centralized crew management that tracks availability, skills, and assignments. Coordinates scheduling across projects, manages timesheets, and ensures proper crew levels for daily work.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Crew assignment and tracking</li>
            <li>Skill-based crew matching</li>
            <li>Timesheet capture and payroll integration</li>
            <li>Availability planning</li>
            <li>Crew productivity analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buyer Profile Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Safety & Compliance Tracking" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Safety & Compliance Tracking</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Safety management that automates compliance checklists, captures incidents and near-misses, tracks corrective actions, and reports safety metrics to leadership and regulators.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Daily safety inspections and checklists</li>
            <li>Incident reporting and investigation</li>
            <li>Corrective action tracking</li>
            <li>Safety metric dashboards</li>
            <li>Regulatory compliance reporting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Market Intelligence -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Project Performance & Profitability" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Project Performance & Profitability</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time project dashboards that track schedule status, budget performance, safety metrics, and quality indicators. Identify projects at risk before they impact profitability.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Schedule performance tracking</li>
            <li>Margin realization reporting</li>
            <li>Quality defect tracking</li>
            <li>Safety performance metrics</li>
            <li>Project profitability forecasting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>

